{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/11463", "repo": "rails", "body": "If you want to do the comparison `begin <= time <= end` you can use the `Range#cover?` method, e.g:\r\n\r\n``` irb\r\n>> range = 10.days.ago..10.days.from_now\r\n=> Sat, 06 Jul 2013 22:56:43 BST +01:00..Fri, 26 Jul 2013 22:56:43 BST +01:00\r\n>> range.cover?(Time.current)\r\n=> true\r\n```\r\n\r\n", "_id": {"$oid": "5237d406bd3543c15100802e"}, "issue_id": 11463, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/21077916", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/11463#issuecomment-21077916", "updated_at": "2013-07-16T22:07:51Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pixeltrix/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pixeltrix/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pixeltrix/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pixeltrix/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/pixeltrix", "login": "pixeltrix", "gravatar_id": "b14001f2b40640dd6cb63f0e8f1f4869", "html_url": "https://github.com/pixeltrix", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pixeltrix/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pixeltrix/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pixeltrix/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/b14001f2b40640dd6cb63f0e8f1f4869?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F7cb36e23529e4de4c41460940cc85e6e.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pixeltrix/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 6321, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pixeltrix/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2013-07-16T22:07:51Z", "id": 21077916, "owner": "rails"}
